            "**Q: How does FoneClaw use AI to manage my notifications?**\nA: FoneClaw employs advanced AI and machine learning to analyze your communication patterns, message content, and personal preferences. It uses this intelligence for **AI notification management**, automatically sorting, prioritizing, summarizing, and filtering messages across various apps. This ensures you only receive relevant alerts when they matter most, reducing digital noise.\n\n**Q: Can FoneClaw summarize emails from any email provider?**\nA: Yes, FoneClaw is designed to integrate with popular email services like Gmail and Outlook. Its **AI email summary** feature works by processing the content of your incoming emails to extract key information and present it to you concisely, regardless of the sender's email provider.\n\n**Q: Is my privacy protected when using AI for message management?**\nA: completely. FoneClaw prioritizes user privacy. All AI processing for features like smart message sorting and reply suggestions occurs securely on your device or through encrypted, anonymized servers. Your personal data is never shared or used for advertising purposes.\n\n**Q: What kind of apps does FoneClaw support for notification management?**\nA: FoneClaw offers comprehensive support for a wide range of communication apps on your Android phone, including iMessage, Gmail, WhatsApp, Slack, and many others. It acts as a central **phone notification organizer** for all your digital interactions, streamlining your entire messaging experience.\n\n**Q: Can I customize how FoneClaw categorizes my messages?**\nA: Yes, FoneClaw offers extensive customization options. While the AI provides intelligent **automatic message categorization** by default, you can easily adjust priorities, create custom categories, and set specific rules using simple voice commands. The agent learns from your feedback to tailor its behavior precisely to your needs."
